<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>صفحه یافت نشد</title>

<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#0c0f1e,#11162f,#1c2444);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: Vazir;
    color: white;
  }

  .box {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    padding: 40px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    text-align: center;
    width: 380px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 55px;
    margin: 0;
    color: #7ec7ff;
  }

  p {
    margin-top: 10px;
    opacity: .85;
  }

  a {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 25px;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#3a88ff,#7ec7ff);
    color: #000;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  a:hover {
    opacity: .85;
  }
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="box">
  <h1>404</h1>
  <p>صفحه مورد نظر یافت نشد.</p>
  <a href="/">بازگشت به صفحه اصلی</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
